sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor KH as Khach hang
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Promotion as Promotion Service
    participant PromotionDB as Promotion DB

    KH->>GW: POST /api/promotions/calculate
    Note over KH,GW: items - productId, quantity, price<br/>customerId, totalAmount
    GW->>Promotion: Forward request - public hoac auth

    Promotion->>PromotionDB: promotion.findAllActive
    Note over Promotion,PromotionDB: status=ACTIVE, startDate <= now<br/>endDate >= now
    PromotionDB-->>Promotion: danh sach promotions dang chay

    loop Moi promotion active
        Promotion->>Promotion: Kiem tra dieu kien ap dung
        Note over Promotion: minOrderAmount, applicableProducts<br/>customerTier, dayOfWeek, timeRange

        alt Promotion khong ap dung duoc
            Note over Promotion: Bo qua promotion nay
        else Promotion ap dung duoc
            Promotion->>Promotion: Tinh appliedAmount
            Note over Promotion: BUY_X_GET_Y - san pham mien phi<br/>PERCENTAGE - giam % tong don<br/>FIXED_AMOUNT - giam so tien co dinh
            Promotion->>Promotion: Them vao danh sach applicable
        end
    end

    Promotion-->>GW: 200 OK
    Note over Promotion,GW: applicablePromotions - danh sach<br/>promotionId, name, appliedAmount<br/>totalDiscount - tong giam gia
    GW-->>KH: Danh sach khuyen mai co the ap dung

    Note over KH,GW: KH chon promotions muon ap dung<br/>Gui promotionIds kem khi checkout

